                    <li>• Live points &amp; comp balances</li>
                    <li>• Win/loss statements</li>
                    <li>• Tier progress &amp; card status</li>
                    <li>• Event &amp; promotion registration</li>
                    <li>• Personalized offers &amp; messaging</li>
