                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Progressive Web App</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    A mobile-first experience that works on any device without app store headaches. Guests add it
                    to their home screen in seconds.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li>• Virtual queues for restaurants, players clubs &amp; events</li>
                    <li>• Digital coupons &amp; offers</li>
                    <li>• Push-style messaging and reminders</li>
                    <li>• Contest &amp; drawing entries</li>
                    <li>• Restaurant reservations and menus</li>
                    <li>• Resilient, offline-aware experience</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Marketing Platform -->
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 rounded-xl bg-[#e8f6fc] flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#ff6b35]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
