                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Real-Time Marketing Platform</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    A direct line to every guest, with complete tracking. Build, schedule, and analyze campaigns
                    from the same platform that powers your portal and PWA.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li>• Targeted campaigns by tier, play, or behavior</li>
                    <li>• Real-time notifications and reminders</li>
                    <li>• Reusable templates for common promotions</li>
                    <li>• Engagement &amp; conversion analytics</li>
                    <li>• Multi-channel reach across web, PWA, SMS, and email</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Feature Grid -->
