                    Replace paper coupons with unique, trackable offers. One-tap redemption, automatic expiration,
                    and real-time reporting come standard.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Interactive Contests -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
