                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Complete Branding Control</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Your colors, your logo, your tone of voice. Update imagery, copy, layouts, and CTA destinations
                    from the admin — no dev backlog, no releases, no app store reviews.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Roadmap / “Always Evolving” -->
        <div class="mt-12 bg-white border border-dashed border-[#3eb3e6] rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:items-center md:justify-between">
                <div>
