                        restaurant integrations are next up.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 md:text-right">
                    Built on the same platform trusted by 70+ properties — no “maybe someday” roadmap items.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

